1204
01:09:36,819 --> 01:09:38,980
- Go on, go on.
- Does he live around here?

1205
01:09:39,055 --> 01:09:42,456
Hamlet. That's really
funny, honey. Bye.

1206
01:09:42,492 --> 01:09:44,551
