- Yeah, so did l...

1229
01:11:01,070 --> 01:11:03,004
but there's concessions
we have to make.

1230
01:11:03,072 --> 01:11:06,041
- The show's a hit.
- She's not the best we could do
for the part.

1231
01:11:06,108 --> 01:11:09,771
- There's plenty other girls around.
